config AMLOGIC_MTD_SPI_NOR
        tristate "AMLOGIC SPI NOR support"
        default n
        help
          This is based on MTD_SPI_NOR, adding partition management.
          Say Y, Will register partitions according to bootargs or dts management.
          Say N, Only register one mtd device.
